{"questionId":"9512","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\\left( x \\right) = \\frac{{4x - 5}}{{{x^2} - 3x + 2}}\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>5</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>3</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>+</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x \\ne 1{\\text{,}}\\,x \\ne 2\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>≠</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Express <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f(x)\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n</math></span> in partial fractions.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\\left( x \\right) = \\frac{{4x - 5}}{{\\left( {x - 1} \\right)\\left( {x - 2} \\right)}} \\equiv \\frac{A}{{x - 1}} + \\frac{B}{{x - 2}}\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>4</mn>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>5</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>1</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>x</mi>\n          <mo>−</mo>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>≡</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>A</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mi>B</mi>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>&nbsp; <em><strong>&nbsp;M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow 4x - 5 \\equiv A\\left( {x - 2} \\right) + B\\left( {x - 1} \\right)\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mn>4</mn>\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>5</mn>\n  <mo>≡</mo>\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x = 1 \\Rightarrow A = 1\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>A</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x = 2 \\Rightarrow B = 3\">\n  <mi>x</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>B</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"f\\left( x \\right) = \\frac{1}{{x - 1}} + \\frac{3}{{x - 2}}\">\n  <mi>f</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>x</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>1</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mfrac>\n    <mn>3</mn>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>x</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><em><strong>[6 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9512","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.3a","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Express f ( x ) in partial fractions.","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 6]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.11—Partial fractions"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}